        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "As they turned again to face the English, some of their Norman horse divided the pursuing body of the English from the rest, and thus all that foremost portion of the English army fell, fighting bravely.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_139681_000022_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/139681/1343_139681_000022_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "The main body still remaining firm, heedless of the Norman arrows, and with their battle axes cutting down the crowds of horsemen when they rode up, like forests of young trees, Duke William pretended to retreat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_139681_000022_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/139681/1343_139681_000022_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "The eager English followed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_139681_000022_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/139681/1343_139681_000022_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "The Norman army closed again, and fell upon them with great slaughter.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_139681_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/139681/1343_139681_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "Shoot upward, Norman archers, that your arrows may fall down upon their faces!'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_139681_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/139681/1343_139681_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "The sun rose high, and sank, and the battle still raged.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_139681_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/139681/1343_139681_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "Through all the wild October day, the clash and din resounded in the air.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_139681_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/139681/1343_139681_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "In the red sunset, and in the white moonlight, heaps upon heaps of dead men lay strewn, a dreadful spectacle, all over the ground.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_139681_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/139681/1343_139681_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "His brothers were already killed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_139681_000025_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/139681/1343_139681_000025_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "The English broke and fled.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_139681_000025_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/139681/1343_139681_000025_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "The Normans rallied, and the day was lost.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "On their journey back to Portray, the ladies were almost too tired for talking; and Sir Griffin was sulky.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "Sir Griffin had as yet heard nothing about Greystock's adventure, and did not care to be told. But when once they were at the castle, and had taken warm baths, and glasses of sherry, and got themselves dressed and had come down to dinner, they were all very happy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000004_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000004_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "And she had by heart every kind word that Lord George had said to her,--and she loved the sweet, pleasant, Corsair like intimacy that had sprung up between them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000004_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000004_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "It was all delightful;--and so much more delightful because mrs Carbuncle had not gone quite so well as she liked to go, and because Lucinda had fallen into the water.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"Yes.\" \"Well?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000005_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000005_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"He proposed; but of course I could not answer him when I was wet through.\" There had been but a moment, and in that moment this was all that Lucinda would say.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"Now I don't mean to stir again,\" said Lizzie, throwing herself into a corner of a sofa, \"till somebody carries me to bed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"You only killed one fox,\" said mr Emilius, pretending a delightfully clerical ignorance, \"and on Monday you killed four.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"About ten, perhaps,\" said Lord George.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"I'm sure it was thirty,\" said Lizzie, forgetting her fatigue in her energy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"It was just whatever is best,\" said Lizzie.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"I know Frank's friend, mr Nappie, said it was twenty.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"I thought so,\" said Frank; \"but I couldn't take the liberty myself.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"I felt that blow,\" said Frank.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"I shall always call you Cousin Greystockings,\" said Lizzie.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "If the horse had been on the roadside, he or his men could have protected him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"It was cruel,\" said Frank.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"If it had happened to me, I should have been very angry,\" said mrs Carbuncle.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"But Frank wouldn't have had a horse at all,\" said Lizzie, \"unless he had taken mr Nappie's.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"There's something in that, certainly; but, still, I agree with mrs Carbuncle.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000023_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000023_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "I can't conceive anything so terrible.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"He'd send you grey stockings instead,\" said Lizzie.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000027_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000027_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "But these Corsairs are known to be dangerous, and it would not be wise that she should sacrifice any future prospect of importance on behalf of a feeling, which, no doubt, was founded on poetry, but which might too probably have no possible beneficial result.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000027_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000027_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "In a ride across the country the Corsair was all that a Corsair should be; but knowing, as she did, but very little of the Corsair, she could not afford to throw over her cousin for his sake.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"It was a matter of course.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1343_158781_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1343/158781/1343_158781_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"I did like it;--and so did you.",
