        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1343",
        "content": "\"As for marrying the widow, I should like to know the facts first. As to mrs c, she wouldn't object in the least.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
